Introduction

The CrewOne was a twelve-member project boy group under IST Entertainment. Consisting of members from ATBO and JUST B, their debut date is currently unknown.

The group name "The CrewOne" symbolizes unity, with members sailing together on the same ship and their fandom name "Journey" means The CrewOne and fans will travel together.

On June 27, 2024, IST Entertainment and Bluedot Entertainment came together to share exciting news. They announced the formation of a project group called ‘The CrewOne’, which symbolizes individuals who have come together as a united ‘crew’ on a single ship. This collaboration brings together two existing groups: ATBO from IST Entertainment and Just B from Bluedot Entertainment. The goal is to create greater synergy and embark on various activities.

They had their first appearance together during a live hosted by ATBO.

On July 20, 2024, Bluedot announced they were putting Siwoo on hiatus for an apparent dating rumor, therefore, for the time being, he is not included in any of the activities.

On November 29, IST Entertainment announced that The CrewOne's collaborative promotions would come to an end and the group is set to disband after the Road to Kingdom : Ace of Ace concert in January 2025. However, as the concert was announced to be canceled on December 2nd, it is safe to assume that the group had effectively disbanded.
